## REIMU'S CURSE REMOVAL — Hakurei Method
*"Yes, fine. Let me look at it."*

**Operator:** Hakurei Reimu

Curse removal through traditional Hakurei shrine maiden techniques. Effective. Efficient. Reimu would rather be doing something else but she does need the donation money.

| Curse Type | Cost |
|---|---|
| Standard D&D Curse (Bestow Curse, Cursed Item) | 100gp |
| Lycanthropy, Mummy Rot | 200gp |
| Touhou — Misfortune (Disadvantage on all d20 rolls) | 150gp |
| Touhou — Bamboo Maze (Cannot benefit from short rests) | 150gp |
| Touhou — Phantom Possession (Wisdom saves vs. brief control) | 250gp |
| Touhou — Time Distortion (Age 1 year per day) | 500gp |
| Touhou — Boundary Confusion (Random 5ft teleport on damage) | 200gp |

**Notes:**
- Reimu accepts donations beyond the listed fee. Her shrine needs maintenance.
- She may quote a higher price when in a bad mood. DC 14 Persuasion to return to standard rate.
- More cooperative when the party's reputation is favorable.